      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後　新MVの撮影日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれから瑠依と優で話し合って、瑠依は）\n（音楽番組の最終回に出ることにした訳だが……）",
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "優はグループの将来を見据えて、トリエルのために\nより話題性のある番組に出るべきだと思ってたんだな",
      "startTime": 13.7666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "優も本音では、三人で最終回に出たかったんです\nだけどトリエルのためを思って我慢して……",
      "startTime": 22.1666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "だから話し合って、優が我慢しなくて済むような\n最高の方法を一緒に考えることにしたんです",
      "startTime": 29.4333331425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その方法が、三人で最終回を盛り上げて\n特番に負けないくらい世間の話題にすること……",
      "startTime": 37.0666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "最終回に三人で出ると決めてから、優はMVの\nアイデアを出したり、最終回用の企画を考えたり……",
      "startTime": 44.9666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろと積極的に動いてくれて、裏番組の特番には\n負けないって張り切ってるんですよ",
      "startTime": 53.4666658401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私が、最終回より特番の方に出るべきだったと\n言われないように……",
      "startTime": 59.8597973462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "この選択は正しかったと胸を張って言えるように\n最高の最終回にしようと燃えているんです",
      "startTime": 65.8333317439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "特番のMCを辞退したことは後悔していないようだな",
      "startTime": 69.0737924973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、しっかり話し合って\n三人で納得して決めましたから",
      "startTime": 75.8000057856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "後悔どころか、優とちゃんとぶつかり合えたことで\n絆がさらに深まった気がします",
      "startTime": 82.4666724522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どんなに仲が良くても\n言葉にしなければ伝わらないこともある……",
      "startTime": 87.3666780471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "信頼している相手だからこそ\n時にはぶつかることも必要だったのかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 93.0666790644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。ぶつかり合って絆がより深まった今なら\n前よりもっといいMVが撮れる気がします",
      "startTime": 101.3666775385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……そろそろ出番ですね。では、行ってきます\n成長した私達の羽ばたきを見ていて下さい",
      "startTime": 108.9333442051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今日の瑠依は、澄み渡る青空のような\nいい表情をしているな",
      "startTime": 117.9333487827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "（新しいMVで表現するのは、羽を広げて）\n（未来へ飛翔するTRINITYAiLEの姿……）",
      "startTime": 124.2000134149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "（『les plumes』を初めて歌った時は）\n（まだ未熟で、こんなに高く飛べなかった）",
      "startTime": 131.0666749952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "（沢山の出会いが、経験が、私達の羽を大きくした）\n（沢山の絆が、私達の羽を強くした）",
      "startTime": 141.7333335238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "（私一人じゃ、この景色まで辿り着けなかった）",
      "startTime": 146.9739585159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（『les plumes』……その羽で）\n（瑠依は俺達にどんな景色を見せてくれるんだ？）",
      "startTime": 155.8333396273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "（この羽なら、どんな未来にも手が届く）\n（この羽があれば、私達はさらなる高みへ羽ばたける）",
      "startTime": 164.7666688917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "（もっと高く、もっと遠く……）\n（希望の羽で、飛び立とう、目指していこう）",
      "startTime": 173.755254658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "（その手をとって連れていくわ）\n（誰も知らない雲の向こうへ）",
      "startTime": 182.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽番組最終回の翌日",
      "startTime": 188.4539761781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のゴールデンタイムの視聴率が出たぞ\n視聴率一位だったのは……例の辞退した特番だ",
      "startTime": 194.2000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……。向こうは宣伝にも相当\n力を入れてましたから、この結果も仕方ありませんね",
      "startTime": 202.8333335241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そう悲観することもないぞ。トリエルが出演した\n音楽番組は、特番に次ぐ視聴率二位だ",
      "startTime": 210.7333335241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "内容もかなり好評で\n最終回にして番組の最高視聴率を更新したらしい",
      "startTime": 216.3666668575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "番組が有終の美を飾れたのなら\n私達も頑張った甲斐がありました",
      "startTime": 223.5000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばSNSでは、最終回とMVの関連ワードが\nトレンドの上位を独占していたそうですね",
      "startTime": 230.8999920528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
