      "text": "分かりました\nどんな内容でも受け入れるので、聞かせて下さい",
      "startTime": 271.566660754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "覚悟は出来ているようだな\nならメッセージを伝えるぞ……",
      "startTime": 278.2333213171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "――新しいMV、とても素晴らしい出来映えで\n改めて天動さんに惚れ込みました",
      "startTime": 285.7333457311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "来年も特番をやることになったら\nぜひMCを引き受けていただきたいです",
      "startTime": 291.2999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "さらに成長した天動さんに会えるのを\n楽しみにしています……だそうだ",
      "startTime": 297.2999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか\n凄くありがたいお話で、光栄です",
      "startTime": 303.0333274205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "このメッセージに返信しようと思うんだが\n瑠依から伝言はあるか？",
      "startTime": 310.7332907993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_03-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "……では、こう伝えて下さい",
      "startTime": 314.5439132765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
